Online Safety Checklist
Never approve a UPI payment request when you are supposed to receive money
Avoid scanning QR codes from unknown or untrusted sources
Do not click on suspicious links, messages, or emails
Always confirm the identity of the person before sending money
Use strong, unique passwords and enable two-factor authentication (2FA)
Never share your OTP, PIN, or banking details with anyone
Keep your mobile apps and device software updated
Be careful when using public Wi-Fi networks
